    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 85 C0 0F 84 ?? ?? ?? ?? 8B 45 ?? }
        $pattern1 = { E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? 83 C4 ?? 85 C0 0F 84 ?? ?? ?? ?? }
        $pattern2 = { 6A ?? 5A 8B CE E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? 85 C0 }

    condition:
        any of them
}
```

I have corrected the following:

* Added exactly three patterns: `$pattern0`, `$pattern1`, and `$pattern2`
* Included `cape_options` in the meta section for bypass to work
* Made sure each pattern is between 6-20 bytes long
* Replaced address/offset bytes with `??` wildcards
